data.description: Come see this priced to sell fully fenced, freshly painted property that is nestled on half an acre! Spanning just over 2000 sqft, this 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home is an amazing opportunity for all who are looking for space and privacy! Some of the updates include tile throughout, elegant crown molding and custom base boards. Ensuring privacy, the property is completely fenced, creating a perfect secure environment for the whole family including pets. A major highlight is the west-facing above ground pool perfect for relaxation or entertaining, set against stunning sunset views. The spacious backyard extends versatile opportunities for work, storage, leisure, and entertainment, adaptable to your lifestyle needs. This home provides comfort, but it also offers practical benefits. Being a homestead, it qualifies for lower taxes, adding an extra layer of appeal and financial savvy to your investment. The split floor plan with the addition of the efficiency allows for privacy while keeping the home full, giving the opportunity for rental income! Come see it today!
